      <title>芝加哥拒绝学区努力支付养老金的债务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-06/chicago-denies-school-district-push-for-debt-to-pay-pension-bill</link>
      <description><![CDATA[芝加哥拒绝承担更多的债务，以平衡其现金短缺的学校制度的预算，否认周三席卷了一个宣传区的领导层。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-06/chicago-denies-school-district-push-for-debt-to-pay-pension-bill</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Mar 2025 17:23:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲央行的负责人摊牌是否在四月是否再次降低利率</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-06/ecb-heads-for-showdown-over-whether-to-cut-rates-again-in-april</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士称，欧洲中央银行官员正在为是否进一步降低利率进行艰难的谈判，或者在4月份设定借贷成本时举行大火。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-06/ecb-heads-for-showdown-over-whether-to-cut-rates-again-in-april</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Mar 2025 17:21:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Bessent说，美国会毫不犹豫地对俄罗斯和伊朗制裁。</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-06/us-won-t-hesitate-on-russia-and-iran-sanctions-bessent-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国财政部长斯科特·贝森特（Scott Bessent）周四表示，如果美国对俄罗斯能源的制裁有助于导致乌克兰战争的停火，那么美国将毫不犹豫地“全力以赴”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-06/us-won-t-hesitate-on-russia-and-iran-sanctions-bessent-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Mar 2025 17:20:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>从GDP排除的美国贸易差距的创纪录贸易差距的黄金进口</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-06/massive-gold-influx-at-root-of-record-us-trade-gap-largely-excluded-from-gdp</link>
      <description><![CDATA[引人注目的进口激增，使美国的贸易赤字陷入了记录，对经济的焦虑提升了其在国际黄金贸易商的疯狂争夺中的根源，将金条赶到了纽约的存放者。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-06/massive-gold-influx-at-root-of-record-us-trade-gap-largely-excluded-from-gdp</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Mar 2025 17:15:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加拿大的Linamar说，关税将使汽车制造商花费数十亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-06/tariffs-will-cost-automakers-billions-says-canada-s-linamar</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大第二大公共汽车零件制造商Linamar Corp.说，向汽车关税增加钢铁和铝关税将使汽车制造商损失数十亿美元，并且“可能会关闭该行业”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-06/tariffs-will-cost-automakers-billions-says-canada-s-linamar</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Mar 2025 17:07:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尼日利亚债券在四个月内以较低的油价下沉</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-06/nigerian-bonds-sink-the-most-in-four-months-on-lower-oil-prices</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尼日利亚美元的债券在近四个月内最糟糕的是，投资者担心石油价格可能会使政府当年的收入预测脱轨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-06/nigerian-bonds-sink-the-most-in-four-months-on-lower-oil-prices</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Mar 2025 17:05:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>债券收益率上升，因为特朗普的关税撤回促进了美国的增长希望</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-06/short-term-treasury-yields-resume-slide-on-whiffs-of-job-losses</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在唐纳德·特朗普总统将墨西哥商品的关税推迟了一个月之后，国债的产量更高，这使美国股票的临时实力震惊。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-06/short-term-treasury-yields-resume-slide-on-whiffs-of-job-losses</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Mar 2025 15:26:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>墨西哥关税延迟，新的制裁前景</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-05/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-march-6</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于交易者称赞美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）的举动推迟了从墨西哥进口的关税，而不是限制伊朗和俄罗斯流动的前景，石油在收益和损失之间翻转。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-05/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-march-6</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Mar 2025 23:29:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>股票沉没作为来源的关税交易：市场包装</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-05/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[华尔街交易员继续在众多关税头条新闻中驾驶激烈，快速，敏锐的市场波动，几乎消除了股票后，股票延长了损失。]]></description>
